{
  "stem": "20609.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I go in the kitchen and I worked with a partner there and I made sure everything was-- and I took my jacket off and I didn't go in the dining room anymore because I didn't have a collar.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The thing just popped open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So now-- and those tuxedos were real heavy, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, they really-- you know,  it was baloney to give that much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was a disaster, that opening night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was a disaster.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The food didn't go out, the kitchen wasn't ready, the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it took-- it got straightened out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We didn't have to wear big collars anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We got a regular tuxedo shirts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So-- but it was a good job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed there till-- till next season and I went back to Florida.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, I became one of those snowbirds, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The minute it got cold, go back to Florida.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, I worked in the Saxony Hotel that just opened up, and Pupi Campo moved over there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And little by little, I got a great job at a place called the Greenbriar Hotel in West Virginia, very famous hotel, and it was owned by the railroad tycoon, Robert-- his name was Robert Young.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always thought it was the actor, but it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he owned the Chesapeake and Ohio Railroad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those are well-- well-financed because they did all the coal-- coal transports, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was a great job, this was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had quarters there, got everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had even a golf course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Unfortunate, I didn't learn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I didn't want to play golf.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sam Snead was the pro out there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I stayed there for about two seasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
